00:01:28,905 --> 00:01:31,781
- They're welcome to come over, <i>mija.</i>
- Thank you, Daddy.

29
00:01:31,784 --> 00:01:33,286
- [HIRAM] Mm-hm.
- Mwah.

30
00:01:35,746 --> 00:01:37,456
