31
00:01:39,249 --> 00:01:41,753
Are we gonna start or
what? Where's Coach Clayton?

32
00:01:41,756 --> 00:01:44,798
- At the hospital with Moose and Midge.
- What?

33
00:01:44,801 --> 00:01:47,831
- Hey, guys!
- [REGGIE] I only know what coach told me.

34
