about how he looked?

88
00:04:43,297 --> 00:04:44,574
[MOOSE] His eyes.

89
00:04:48,021 --> 00:04:49,231
They're green, right?

90
00:04:50,032 --> 00:04:51,316
[MIDGE] They were blank.

91
00:04:52,609 --> 00:04:54,861
Like there wasn't a person behind them.

92
00:04:57,022 --> 00:05:00,234
He was like Michael Myers.
He had the devil's eyes.

93
00:05:02,164 --> 00:05:03,411
[MIDGE SIGHS]

94
00:05:06,206 --> 00:05:08,998
[METAL DETECTOR BEEPING]

95
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,753
- It's the pins on my hat.
- Take it off, go again.

96
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:21,907
Forsythe Pendleton Jones III.

97
00:05:21,910 --> 00:05:24,977
Uh... it's Jughead, actually.

98
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,107
I'm Toni Topaz.

99
00:05:26,948 --> 00:05:30,388
I was supposed to give you
the full animatronic tour,

100
00:05:30,391 --> 00:05:33,856
but some robots went insane
and started killing the guests,

101
00:05:33,858 --> 00:05:35,969
so, we'll just wing it.

102
00:05:37,552 --> 00:05:41,012
Classrooms don't have Wi-Fi,
bathroom stalls don't have doors.

103
00:05:41,015 --> 00:05:42,932
What about the <i>Red and Black?</i>

104
00:05:42,935 --> 00:05:47,062
Yeah, it no longer exists. Censorship?
Budget cuts? Take your pick.

105
00:05:47,065 --> 00:05:52,652
You'll find a glimpse of jingle-jangle
being consumed in its natural habitat.

106
00:05:52,655 --> 00:05:54,835
[JUGHEAD] I'm sorry, "jingle-jangle"?

107
00:05:54,838 --> 00:05:59,549
This place is crawling with the JJ.
A highly addictive total gutter drug.

108
00:05:59,551 --> 00:06:01,641
So, let's not touch that.

109
00:06:02,485 --> 00:06:03,722
Jingle-jangle.

110
00:06:04,485 --> 00:06:06,071
Fascinating.

111
00:06:06,074 --> 00:06:09,434
[TONI] All right. Here in the cafetorium,
Ghoulies sit over there.

112
00:06:09,436 --> 00:06:13,896
Rival gang, drug dealers, street
racers, rumors of cannibalism.

113
00:06:13,899 --> 00:06:15,681
Don't ask.

114
00:06:15,684 --> 00:06:18,602
And we sit over there.
With the Serpents.

115
00:06:18,605 --> 00:06:20,493
You're a Southside Serpent?

116
00:06:20,496 --> 00:06:23,624
Why do you think that I
volunteered to give you the tour?

117
00:06:24,659 --> 00:06:27,201
Actually, I'm gonna sit alone.

118
00:06:27,203 --> 00:06:30,332
Just, you know, finish
my book and brood.

119
00:06:30,967 --> 00:06:34,093
I'm confused. Aren't you
like a Serpent by blood?

120
00:06:34,096 --> 00:06:36,305
The son of FP Jones?

121
00:06:36,308 --> 00:06:37,682
Yeah.

122
00:06:37,685 --> 00:06:42,438
So, I self-identify as a
loner, not a pack animal.

123
00:06:42,441 --> 00:06:46,318
I'm just gonna put my head down
and try and get through this, okay?

124
00:06:46,321 --> 00:06:51,086
Hey, you wanna get through this,
you should hang with the Serpents.

125
00:06:52,103 --> 00:06:55,104
If the Ghoulies get a whiff that
you're alone, or vulnerable,

126
00:06:55,106 --> 00:06:59,360
