you can say <i>American History X.</i>

127
00:07:03,073 --> 00:07:06,864
Moose and Midge described him. Same
guy that shot you, same hood, eyes.

128
00:07:06,867 --> 00:07:08,935
Well, maybe and maybe not.

129
00:07:08,938 --> 00:07:10,548
Dad, it's him.

130
00:07:10,551 --> 00:07:15,239
If Sheriff Keller's not gonna take that
seriously, I think we should... be ready.

131
00:07:15,242 --> 00:07:19,703
Like, maybe we should buy a
gun, just be armed in case...

132
00:07:19,706 --> 00:07:20,879
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

133
00:07:20,882 --> 00:07:24,678
Easy, okay? Ease up on that. We're
gonna let the cops do their job.

134
00:07:25,410 --> 00:07:28,428
