136
00:07:29,938 --> 00:07:33,544
We don't keep guns in this house. Okay?

137
00:07:33,547 --> 00:07:34,813
So, just cool it.

138
00:07:38,103 --> 00:07:40,563
Why don't you sit down
next to me, loverboy?

139
00:07:42,112 --> 00:07:45,988
- Archie?
