144
00:07:56,835 --> 00:07:58,251
[JUGHEAD] No, don't stop him.

145
00:07:58,253 --> 00:08:01,145
Archie going Travis Bickle
is my favorite Archie yet.

146
00:08:01,148 --> 00:08:04,860
Doesn't it feel like he's
targeting us? I mean, specifically?

147
00:08:06,177 --> 00:08:08,388
I don't want anyone else getting hurt.

148
00:08:08,391 --> 00:08:11,349
