- Hi. Nice to meet you.

155
00:08:29,254 --> 00:08:30,906
[VERONICA] And Jughead Jones.

156
00:08:30,909 --> 00:08:31,825
- Hi.
- [HIRAM] Hey.

157
00:08:31,828 --> 00:08:34,162
- You know my dad.
- [HIRAM] I do. He's a good man.

158
00:08:34,164 --> 00:08:35,204
He values family.

159
00:08:35,206 --> 00:08:38,040
I hope his return comes
sooner rather than later.

160
00:08:38,042 --> 00:08:40,376
- Yeah, so do we.
- [VERONICA] And, Daddy, this is...

161
00:08:40,378 --> 00:08:43,590
Archie Andrews. The boy who's
captured my daughter's heart.

162
00:08:44,257 --> 00:08:47,122
- Daddy.
- Uh, it's nice to meet you, sir.

163
00:08:47,125 --> 00:08:48,334
Ah, please.

164
00:08:49,651 --> 00:08:50,694
Call me Hiram.

165
00:08:53,269 --> 00:08:56,729
I couldn't help but overhear
your discussion and I, um...

166
00:08:56,732 --> 00:08:59,227
