aren't always the solution.

170
00:09:08,490 --> 00:09:12,617
Sometimes we need to take
matters into our own hands.

171
00:09:12,619 --> 00:09:15,692
- We need to protect ourselves.
- [HERMIONE] We're gonna lose our table.

172
00:09:15,695 --> 00:09:17,064
Oh, yes, of course.

173
00:09:17,067 --> 00:09:19,435
Hey, it was nice to meet all of you.

174
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:24,545
- Oh, and Archie.
- Yes.

175
00:09:24,547 --> 00:09:27,067
[HIRAM] Why don't you
come over for dinner this weak?

176
00:09:27,070 --> 00:09:30,740
I look forward to seeing what you
come up with... to save Riverdale.

